          "reviewBody": "There are serious concerns which needs to be addressed by the school management:\n\n1. Tuition Fee hikes every year and is on a higher side. Transportation fees are also higher and increase every year.\n\n2. Teachers are changing every academic year.\n\n3. There is no proper coordination between teacher, student and parent.\n\n4. School management and Principal are not easily accessible, I have tried to meet but still not got the opportunity.\n\n5. School uniforms and material are of low quality and costly too.",
