          "reviewBody": "\"Annual day function 1 Feb 2025 Giis Balewadi feedback\" Class K2A\nThe student performances were captivating and showcased a wide range of talents, demonstrating great dedication and practice. The stage design and decorations were visually stunning, perfectly complementing the theme of the event(Topsy turvy) .  Appreciation for the teacher's ( *specially class teachers Ashwini and Shalini ma'am and co-ordinator Priya Johri ma'am* ) hard work and dedication in preparing the students for such a remarkable show. Thank you to all the teachers and staff members. Curiously waiting for the photos and videos.",
          "publisher": {
